fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"d3bf1fc53c","type":"paragraph","text":"X人民公社将来要集中种蔬荣，种蔬荣也要专业化。","index":20,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"8e28690177","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":21,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"6841baaf2e","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":22,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"dd7babe743","type":"paragraph","text":"X（毛主席在参观除四害陈列馆时说）老鼠这个东西很较滑，这样，老鼠就要大遗殊啦","index":23,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"40eb3412be","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":24,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"acf50eca5f","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":25,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"4160615466","type":"paragraph","text":"X人民公社好，人民公社好。","index":26,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"e1e23c0fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":27,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"1681a4eea6","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":28,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"7de8d7bab8","type":"paragraph","text":"X….以后山坡上要多开开茶园。","index":29,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"aab81a6564","type":"paragraph","text":"（祝察合肥时的鼓话）","index":30,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"071c22b9cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年九月）（毛主席到合肥时高兴地说）沿途一望，生气勃勃，肯定是有希望的，有大希望的。","index":31,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"fb6029a4c7"},{"id":"b2f006b65a","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛主席在与妇女干部谈话时说）如果每年每人没有一千斤，两千斤粮食，没有公共食堂，没有幸福院托儿所，没有扫除文育，没有进小学，中学，大学，妇女还不可能彻底解放。","index":32,"publicationId":"b